      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/gd9OkfsZiZ%2f1752484841328%2f%e1%9e%96%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9f%87%e1%9e%85%e1%9f%90%e1%9e%93%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%91%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%b7%e1%9e%84%e1%9e%98%e1%9e%bd%e1%9e%80%2fThe+Moon+and+The+Cap_Page+041.jpg",
      "text": "នៅតាមផ្លូវទៅផ្ទះ ខ្យល់បក់ខ្លាំង។ វាបានបំផ្ទុះមួករបស់ខ្ញុំ។"
    },
